Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right. You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:38.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Retreat! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you let him get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:01:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's losing it. It won't be much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:01:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finish him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is as it should be.
