Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We failed again on our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should be saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy, you're slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to say\Nthings like "failed mission"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...or "missed opportunity"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...or that it was a "complete screw up."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never say that in front of you-know-who.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that right?\NYou're talking about Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It didn't occur to me. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not occur to you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:02.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to apologize to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, at least we were able to confirm\Nthere's a major demon here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't call it a complete failure\Neven though a demon didn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's actually better that a\Nmajor demon doesn't appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to keep telling me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's the matter?!\NCome on! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poor thing. What a terrible injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably escaped\Nfrom the Black Steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Based on the injury, anyway.\NBut look at this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a scar from an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do those Black Steel think\Nthey're doing, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They call themselves assassins,\Nbut they always keep their demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys... We meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to take this opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...to cut me down right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gremlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everybody, out front! Get out front!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me the giant\Ndemon Ayano saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...was actually you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gremlin! But, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to stop him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the\NBlack Steel did to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...but all I can say now is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that gremlin doesn't exist anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mr. Gremlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gremlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I won't be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...cause you all any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did the Black Steel do this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:06:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That after I became a great demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I could've kept on smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I did that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I wouldn't have been\Nhated by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really screwed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gremlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the number of sex murders\Ncaused by demons has gone up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though we're working\Nso hard to get rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could only mean that the\Nnumber of demons has been rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where could they all be coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About a year ago, there were\Na number of incidents...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...where some members\Nof the Kagemai died...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...leaving messages\Nabout becoming demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still don't know the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's said that my step brother\Nwas in the Kagemai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and that he died fighting a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:13.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not exactly true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother was a bright,\Nstrong and dependable Kagemai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear brother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A demon... A demon's possessed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:08:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A demon has possessed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The demon...! The demon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misaki, I'm finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NYou're just tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave your dinner here,\Nso make sure you eat. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just know it. I'm going\Nto turn into a demon soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been possessed by a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could something like\Nthat happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's actually happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those sure look tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:09:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want me to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By wanting me to stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...you mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not your brother anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, let's not get all hung up with\Nthings. Let's enjoy ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please, stop! Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What have I... What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I learned later...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that my brother had\Ninvestigated the Black Steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was also...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like what happened to that gremlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misaki, thanks for telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to destroy the Black Steel?\NAre you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:57.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just don't like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got to calm down, Rekka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel, but that's\Nstill no excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like the Crimson Lotus, the Black\NSteel's aim is to fight demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not right for one to be so hateful\Nof the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're not required to state publicly\Nwhat their activities are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...so even if you asked the Elder,\Nyou wouldn't find out what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to go, anyway. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to Kigan Castle,\Nwhere they're based, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not one to give up, no matter\Nhow much I try to stop you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsukikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, come back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsukikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed, Rekka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's pointless heading\Noff into the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about I lead you in from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you Black Steel\Ngive us a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Akagane.\NI have sworn my allegiance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...to Lord Yasha,\Nthe leader of the Black Steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I've been having some second\Nthoughts about this recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are moments when I succumb to\Nemotion like you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That may actually be a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I question whether I should continue as\Na Black Steel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...after my hesitation, I thought I'd\Nleave it to you to decide for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I let the gremlin go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is the Black Steel up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to see with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A secret factory run by the Black Steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akagane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those people are of the Crimson Lotus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking of\Nbetraying Lord Yasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gennai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't a question of\Nloyalty and betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is so that I can clear the\Nconfusion in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel it as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Confusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of confusion could there be\Nin this superhuman research?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The beautiful children\Nthat I have created.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The result of my\Nlong years of research.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By fusing humans and demons into one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...one can create a superhuman\Nrace that combines the...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...intelligence of humans with the\Nviolent instincts of the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superhuman race?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Black Steel is a\Nsuperhuman organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our goals are to develop\Na true superhuman race...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that goes well beyond the\Ncapabilities of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this why you always kept\Nthe demons you defeated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then why don't\Nyou take the form of a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The research is not yet complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you fuse humans and\Ndemons together...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...in the worst case, one's spirit gets\Ntaken away by the demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and one simply turns\Ninto a pure demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:48.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, we dispose of\Nall of the defective ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, we release\Nthem into the wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, there're more demons out there\Nbecause they're made here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think I'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't play stupid with me!\NHow dare you play with human lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You will pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...will never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same goes for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akagane! Stop this! Make them stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really did betray me this time,\Ndidn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:48.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Yama, my greatest achievement!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:17:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It will become the new superhuman race!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Yama! Eliminate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woman...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Yama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gennai, give me back my woman's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that after seeing a\Nwoman's body after all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...human memories are coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woman... Gennai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me back my woman's body!\NGive it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's coming! It's rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fire's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lord Yasha is in the main keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akagane! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirogane...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My confusion has cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cannot allow the Black Steel\Nto continue existing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you're ready to\Nbear the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you Yasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Yasha, the leader\Nof the Black Steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you the Crimson Lotus\Nwho have come to destroy us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Rekka, leader of the anti-demon\Nbrigade Crimson Lotus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in favor of the plan to capture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and gather demons and\Nfuse them with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without the mental power\Nneeded to beat the demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...one becomes simply possessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and then turns into the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A great power that can protect\Nthis land from the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Learning of what my desires were,\Nthe Great Elder invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To go "beyond mere human."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What great power?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because of sentiments like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:58.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that I have an opportunity to emerge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that's what it was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was the demons that had\Nled the Black Steel astray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what will you do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akagane, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has the Black Steel been\Nwrong all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there were times\Nwhen we were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we had strayed from\Nour course without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since we have sworn allegiance to\NLord Yasha, there was no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akagane...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must follow the path\Nthat you believe is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose this is the limit\Nof your human strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.41,0:22:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how about myself,\Nwho has the blood of demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akagane!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akagane!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.33,0:22:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're the great sorcerer\Nfrom back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the one who killed my father\Nthe demon fighter 4 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All those innocent\Npeople of the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I invited him to join me\Nand go beyond being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The foolish man refused me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:22:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:00.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,0:23:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm? This woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall avenge the deaths...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...of my father and the villagers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.91,0:23:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.98,0:24:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:24:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came home, Rekka!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.78,0:24:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsukikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.56,0:24:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsukikage, we're together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.86,0:24:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.67,0:24:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll always be together, Rekka.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.24,0:24:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.33,0:26:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this all about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.33,0:26:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.67,0:26:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.87,0:26:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to rule the entire world\Nas soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.34,0:26:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.11,0:27:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder how she was able to\Ndraw out the demon within her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.48,0:27:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows. Let's just pray that...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.65,0:27:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that people like that\Ndon't appear again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.72,0:27:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think a lot of people\Nwould be saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.15,0:27:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...now that the Black Steel is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.96,0:27:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If something like that appears again...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.79,0:27:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...we just have to go and destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.79,0:27:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.06,0:27:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.57,0:27:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's exactly right.